   <text>
      <body>
         <pb/>
         <milestone n="92" unit="page"/>
         <lb/>
         <lb/>
         <head>
            <emph>LINES <lb/>
               <lb/>Written in early Spring.<lb/>
               <lb/>
            </emph>
         </head>
         <lg n="1" type="stanza">
            <l n="1">I heard a thousand blended notes, </l>
            <l n="2">While in a grove I sate reclined,</l>
            <l n="3">In that sweet mood when pleasant thoughts</l>
            <l n="4">Bring sad thoughts to the mind.</l>
         </lg>
         <lg n="2" type="stanza">
            <l n="5">To her fair works did nature link</l>
            <l n="6">The human soul that through me ran ;</l>
            <l n="7">And much it griev’d my heart to think</l>
            <l n="8">What man has made of man.</l>
         </lg>
         <pb/>
         <milestone n="93" unit="page"/>
         <lb/>
         <lb/>
         <lg n="3" type="stanza">
            <l n="9">Through primrose tufts, in that sweet bower,</l>
            <l n="10">The periwinkle trail’d its wreathes ;</l>
            <l n="11">And ’tis my faith that every flower</l>
            <l n="12">Enjoys the air it breathes.</l>
         </lg>
         <lg n="4" type="stanza">
            <l n="13">The birds around me hopp’d and play’d :</l>
            <l n="14">Their thoughts I cannot measure,</l>
            <l n="15">But the least motion which they made,</l>
            <l n="16">It seem’d a thrill of pleasure.</l>
         </lg>
         <lg n="5" type="stanza">
            <l n="17">The budding twigs spread out their fan,</l>
            <l n="18">To catch the breezy air ;</l>
            <l n="19">And I must think, do all I can, </l>
            <l n="20">That there was pleasure there.</l>
         </lg>
         <lg n="6" type="stanza">
            <l n="21">If I these thoughts may not prevent,</l>
            <l n="22">If such be of my creed the plan,</l>
            <l n="23">Have I not reason to lament</l>
            <l n="24">What man has made of man ?</l>
         </lg>
      </body>
   </text>
